# Force LF for files where CRLF would break consumers.
#
# `git apply` treats each line in a patch literally; CRLF context lines
# do not match the LF lines in the upstream Odoo file and the patch
# fails. Same for shell scripts (rc.local, helper bins) which are
# executed on the Pi (Linux).
*.patch       text eol=lf
*.sh          text eol=lf
src/etc/**    text eol=lf
src/usr/**    text eol=lf
